{"type":"text","timestamp":1778523909039,"sessionID":"ses_1e7d04012ffeKDuED53D0M0lwn","part":{"id":"prt_e18485e2e001tSKnJeCZHBRIdI","messageID":"msg_e18485bcb001vqvhehM0OFcAHO","sessionID":"ses_1e7d04012ffeKDuED53D0M0lwn","type":"text","text":"---\n## ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nChanges committed in PR #<NN>.\n\n## PR_COMMENTS.md\nThe following changes were made to the UBERON ontology:\n\n1.  **Esophagus (UBERON:0001043)**: Removed the `relationship: located_in UBERON:0002224 ! thoracic cavity` axiom. This is because the esophagus has cervical and abdominal parts in humans, so it is not exclusively located in the thoracic cavity.\n2.  **Esophageal artery (UBERON:0035539)**: Updated the relationship from `branching_part_of` to `connecting_branch_of` for the thoracic aorta (UBERON:0001515).\n\n### Validation\n- Verified that `connecting_branch_of` is a used relationship type in the ontology (checked via grep).\n- Verified the changes using `obo-grep.pl` before committing.\n- Checked out terms using `obo-checkout.pl` and checked in using `obo-checkin.pl`.\n- Note: `robot convert` failed because the `robot` command was not found in the environment, but the edits were successfully applied to `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.","time":{"start":1778523856430,"end":1778523909036}}}
